{"tid":2163250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如何破解臨立會2.0嘅分化？","createTime":"2020-08-18T14:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T15:08:39.000Z","uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"64bff8c5b9d435b6a3f57aca46d399f0d1bac2ee","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"DQ 公民黨就係先將泛民同本土抗爭炒埋一碟，然後就讓這四名議員延任就造成分化。<br />\n<br />\n與其單純爭論去定留，可否想像去或留嘅抗爭後路？<br />\n<br />\n就以留來說，可否以留任議員聘請初選勝出嘅參選人做助理，然後讓佢哋喺議會工作/曝光，以解决去留嘅分歧。"},{"pid":"c953d440f4f50a4b30341ea8d02b7cf3b2c85759","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4042fde5befcdd1ea99a42d53b690e6d897c8cbd","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"249613bc20b2b23f05d9bf59020f02a6f1ab248d","tid":2163250,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"總辭與留任以外第三條路： 初選勝者指示泛民投票，泛民薪津悉數交出<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aBsnzwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aBsnzwU</a>"},{"pid":"fd2f9ad3de8c47b0d9ba70fe983954cd2e91c030","tid":2163250,"uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"召開初選勝出者會議決定去留對策，直播辯論、記名表決。有決定之後就同心遵從，避免陷入無止境嘅爭論與撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n去留之爭唯一解方：請初選勝出者盡快召開會議決定去留對策<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2163103\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2163103</a>"},{"pid":"d1de7de8297b0e7ff15d8497949f8032c5cbd060","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a7ac3498a2d0a1e236984a13e23294cb1c503e67","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"252b289ce8c3b993b27d7193f6d6ca9668b71010","tid":2163250,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":